magic.misc19.caster_root.description: An impartation of visions related to its caster
magic.misc19.target_root.description: An impartation of visions related to its caster's target
magic.misc19.position_root.description: An impartation of visions related to its place in the world
magic.misc19.second_hertz.description: Calls upon the spell each second
magic.misc19.minute_hertz.description: Calls upon the spell once per minute
magic.misc19.basic_circle.description: An extension of the arrangement that enacts itself when called upon
magic.misc19.step_circle.description: An extension of the arrangement that enacts a portion of itself when called upon
magic.misc19.two_sigil.description: A vision of twins, pairs, and partners
magic.misc19.four_sigil.description: A vision of families, parties, and carriage wheels
magic.misc19.eight_sigil.description: A vision of gatherings, companies, and bands
magic.misc19.sixteen_sigil.description: A vision of kingdoms, castles, and palaces
magic.misc19.pi_sigil.description: A vision of the quintessential precept for drawing circles
magic.misc19.xyz_sigil.description: A vision of a tower with doorways to all paths
magic.misc19.down_sigil.description: A vision of a path descending to the ground
magic.misc19.up_sigil.description: A vision of a path ascending into the air
magic.misc19.north_sigil.description: A vision of a path marching backwards
magic.misc19.south_sigil.description: A vision of a path marching forwards
magic.misc19.east_sigil.description: A vision of a path approaching the rising sun
magic.misc19.west_sigil.description: A vision of a path approaching the setting sun
magic.misc19.local_sigil.description: Appeals to %s to bear or impart a vision
magic.misc19.age_sigil.description: A vision of the arrangement's presence through time
magic.misc19.caster_sigil.description: A vision of the arrangement's caster
magic.misc19.position_sigil.description: A vision of the arrangement's place in the world
magic.misc19.target_sigil.description: A vision of the caster's point of focus
magic.misc19.look_sigil.description: A vision of the caster's gaze
magic.misc19.index_sigil.description: A vision of a circle's presence in time
magic.misc19.continue_sigil.description: A vision of the arrangement extending forward in time
magic.misc19.origo_element.description: The element of life, creation, and vitality
magic.misc19.mundus_element.description: The element of the Overworld, earth, and stone
magic.misc19.ardere_element.description: The element of the Nether, burning, and passion
magic.misc19.mare_element.description: The element of the ocean, obfuscation, and protection
magic.misc19.finis_element.description: The element of the End, motion, and decomposition
magic.misc19.sculk_element.description: The element of unmaking, silence, and inertia
magic.misc19.set_glyph.description: Carries a vision to a point where it can be retrieved later
magic.misc19.add_glyph.description: Combines two or more visions into one
magic.misc19.sub_glyph.description: Refines one vision to exclude another
magic.misc19.div_glyph.description: Separates one vision into its occurences of another
magic.misc19.mod_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of what remains when another is divided
magic.misc19.random_glyph.description: Imparts a vision selected randomly from a selection
magic.misc19.equals_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of truth when all visions are equal
magic.misc19.and_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of truth when all visions are true
magic.misc19.or_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of truth when any visions is true
magic.misc19.xor_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of truth when only one vision is true
magic.misc19.not_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of truth when all visions are false
magic.misc19.greater_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of truth when one vision is more potent than the next
magic.misc19.lesser_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of truth when one vision is less potent than the next
magic.misc19.make_vec_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of a new path
magic.misc19.dot_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of two paths entwining
magic.misc19.cross_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of two paths diverging
magic.misc19.normalize_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of a single step on a path
magic.misc19.length_glyph.description: Imparts a vision of the length of a path
magic.misc19.entity_position_glyph.descr: Imparts a vision of a creature's location
magic.misc19.entity_velocity_glyph.descr: Imparts a vision of a creature's direction of motion
magic.misc19.entity_look_glyph.descripti: Imparts a vision of a creature's gaze
magic.misc19.entity_health_glyph.descrip: Imparts a vision of a creature's gaze
magic.misc19.entity_target_glyph.descrip: Imparts a vision of a creature's target
magic.misc19.stack_get_glyph.description: Imparts a vision seen through a door in a tower
magic.misc19.stack_add_glyph.description: Carries a vision to be held within a tower with others of its nature
magic.misc19.stack_sub_glyph.description: Removes a vision from its place within a tower
magic.misc19.debug_function.description: Notifies the creator of all visions held within it
magic.misc19.motion_function.description: Directs a creature down a path.
magic.misc19.creation_function.descripti: Coalesces magical energy at a given point to form a material construct
magic.misc19.dispel_function.description: Dissipates active magical energy within an area around a point
magic.misc19.potion_function.description: Entwines magical energy into a creature for a variety of results
